# ======================
# TEAMS ENDPOINTS
# ======================

### Get All Teams
GET {{F1Sim.Api_HostAddress}}/api/teams
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Team by ID
GET {{F1Sim.Api_HostAddress}}/api/teams/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create Team - Mercedes
POST {{F1Sim.Api_HostAddress}}/api/teams
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mercedes-AMG Petronas F1 Team",
  "constructor": "Mercedes",
  "foundedYear": 2010,
  "baseLocation": "Brackley, United Kingdom",
  "championshipsWon": 8
}

